quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  25,3,"∆Āe njogitii ga makko dewetee…ói …ói tagaani hu'unde kannji ko …ói tagaa…ói, …ói maranah ko'e majji lorra wonaa nafa …ói marah maayde wonaa ngurndam wonaa ummital."
  25,4,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe mbi'i: "Ndee [Alqur'aanaare] wonaani si wona pene …ói o fekindii …óum, walli mo e hoore majje yim…ďe goo". GooŇč…óii …ďe ngaddii too√Īe e bagamma."
  25,5,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko nde tinndi adinoo…ďe o mbinnditi …ói hi…ói fidanee mo bimmbi e kiikii…óe"."
  25,6,"Maaku: "Jippinii nde on ganndu…óo ngunndoo on ka kammuuli e ka leydi, pellet, KaŇčko o Laatike cuhroowo jurmetee…óo metee…óo"."
  25,7,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Ko he…ďi oo Nulaa…óo, homo √Īaama √Īaametee homo yaha kadi ka lokooji(jeereeji)¬į? Ko haanunoo ko nde jippintee e makko Maleykaaji o laatoo wond'ude e makko jeertinoowo"."
  25,8,"Ma werlee e makko ngal, ma laatanoo mo ngesa o √Īaama e mabba. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďen mbi'i: "on njokkaani si wonaa gorko mbil…óaa…óo.""
  25,9,"Ndaarii [yo Nulaa…óo] ko honno …ďe piyiranat maa mise, …ďe majjii …ďe hattantaake [he…ďude] laawol."
  25,10,"Mawnii on taw…óo si O muuyii O wa…óane mo∆ī∆īere, no e …óum gese no ila ley majje can…óe …óen, o wa…óane kadi ku…ďeeje."
  25,11,"Ko woni, …ďe njeddu Darngo ngo, Min heblorani …ďen jeddu…ďe Darngal ngal Yiite ooynge."